*======================================= CHAT RC ======================================*

						<SSL> CHAT RC by Jad Rayes ( JAVA SE 8 )  
									Version 1.0 ALPHA.
						Securely Log in and chat with your friends. 
						
						
						
USAGE 
One user acts as a server the rest as clients. Multiple connections are supported by Java's
threading API. Server is only configured to run locally. To change this edit Server.java, and replace HOST,
and PORT with the appropriate values.
A CLI and GUI exist for this service, and has not yet been deployed.

GOALS OF DEVELOPMENT 
Make connections more secure and incorporate SSL. 


KNOWN BUGS AND ISSUES 
Issues encountered with the DBMS, specifically ORACLE. Switched to MYSQL.
